title: CRED REA Fish Team Stationary Point Count Surveys at Ofu-Olosega, American Samoa, 2006
name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-ofu-olosega-american-samoa-2006
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments (REA) conducted at 12 sites around Ofu-Olosega in the American Samoa (AS) during "February 9 - March 10, 2006" in the NOAA Hi'ialakai (HI0602) Reef Assessment and Monitoring Program (RAMP) Cruise. Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
